<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">&nbsp;</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<div>
<p>故事的标题来自詹姆斯·泰勒的《火与雨》。我针对内容做了一些处理。在此致歉。</p>
</div>
<hr />
<div id="u-author_block">
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><span class="logical-link-wrap"><a href="/dr-cimmerian-s-personnel-file">dr-cimmerian-s-personnel-file</a><span class="logical-link-internal logical-link-internal-false"><span class="logical-link-title logical-link-link-true"><a href="/dr-cimmerian-s-personnel-file">Dr. Cimmerian的人事档案</a></span><span class="logical-link-custom logical-link-link-true"><a href="/dr-cimmerian-s-personnel-file">▸ 该作者的更多作品 ◂</a></span></span><span class="logical-link-original logical-link-original-false"><span class="logical-link-appended">（<a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/dr-cimmerian-s-personnel-file">原文链接</a>）</span><span class="logical-link-title logical-link-link-true"><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/dr-cimmerian-s-personnel-file">dr-cimmerian-s-personnel-file</a></span><span class="logical-link-custom logical-link-link-true"><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/dr-cimmerian-s-personnel-file">▸ 该作者的更多作品 ◂</a></span></span><span class="logical-link-mark-common logical-link-mark-mark-false" style="color: #009966"><sup><span class="fa fa-link"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;</span></span></sup></span><span class="logical-link-mark-newpage logical-link-mark-mark-false" style="color: #F00"><sup><span class="fa fa-link"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;</span></span></sup></span></span></p>
</div>
<hr /></div>
<div class="translation_block">
<h1 id="toc0"><span>其他语言</span></h1>
<div class="list-pages-box">    <div class="list-pages-item">


<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--files/nav%3Aside/interwikiFrame.html?category=_default&amp;pagename=sweet-dreams-and-flying-machines-in-pieces-on-the-ground" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="" style=""></iframe></p>
</div>
    
    
    
    </div></div>
<div class="u-faq">
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="/component:info-ayers">常见问题</a></p>
</div>
